<plot>On one hand the story of the filmmakers' obsession with a shining cultural icon - a gigantic neon Coca-Cola Sign - and at the same time a series of meticulously constructed TV commercial simulations, with a parade of characters and situations that comment on The Sign - from its domination of the public landscape down to its influence on the personal "impulse" for pleasure, the veritable will to "enjoy."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?178898</url></doc>
